  <tr>
    <td align="left" valign="top"><font face="Verdana" size="2">
    Used for the Armor of Ro. You need Sands of Ro, Granite from MM, 2 ench plat bars, Soil of the Underfoot, and melatite. You then combine them in a bag recieved from the Temple of Solusek Ro.

--Rendeli ArdorHeart
HighKnight of Honor in
The Seven Virtues</font>
    </td>
  </tr>
  
