				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Information on Bar of Ro<BR>
<BR>
Mistmore Granite (No Drop, Flouting Gargs are best)<BR>
Melatite (This can be bought from players for around 10-50pp depending on how much they know paladins need this.  This is found on Sol A of Clockworks.)<BR>
Sands of Ro (This can also be bought off players for about 10-20pp, found in Oasis or So Ro off SG's)<BR>
Fairy Dust (This can be bought for around 2-5pp and can be found in LFay, need 4 to be turned into soil of the underfoot NO DROP off Fairy's)<BR>
Enchanted Bars of Plat (Bought of Jewelers but need to be enchanted by enchanters about 100pp each)<BR>
<BR>
Cyclopes Skulls can be traded. 10-20pp each<BR>
(Helm)<BR>
BBK Plans can be traded. 50pp each<BR>
(Boots)<BR>
Night Fall Giant Head can be traded. 50pp each<BR>
(Greaves)<BR>
Deepwaternets are NO DROP.<BR>
(Guantlets)<BR>
Cook Cauldrons are NO DROP.<BR>
(Breatplate)<BR>
Deseased Shark Skin are NO DROP.<BR>
(Vambracers)<BR>
Sentry Alchin Locket is NO DROP.<BR>
(Guantlets)<BR>
<BR>
Ronium bars can be bought once they are complete, but I sell mine for 750-1k.  So it is a lot cheaper to make then if you want to take the time.  I have almost a full suit, but I need one more cauldron.<BR>
<BR>
I am on the Luclin server if anyone of you need help getting your pieces.<BR>
<BR>
Hope this helps...<BR>
<BR>
Turner Trueblade
				</font>
			</td>

